## 🔧 Generación Rápida de Secretos

```bash
# SESSION_SECRET
echo "SESSION_SECRET=$(openssl rand -base64 32)"

# OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET
echo "OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET=$(openssl rand -base64 32)"

# O ambos a la vez
echo "SESSION_SECRET=$(openssl rand -base64 32)" >> backend/.env
echo "OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET=$(openssl rand -base64 32)" >> backend/.env
```

